---
title: Sweet Chilli Glazed Cheese and Spicy Aioli with jewelled couscous
description: The golden cheese in this recipe is coated with a mix of Middle Eastern spices and glazed in sumptuous sweet chilli sauce, while a bed of couscous forms the base of this vibrant veggie dish.
